  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### AI Agent with Geomelon as a tool\nGeomelon is tool-enabled (`usableAsTool`), so it can be wired straight into an AI Agent's tool list — the agent decides which resource/operation to call from the chat message. Requires an OpenAI credential on the Chat Model node and a Geomelon API (RapidAPI) credential on the Geomelon node.",
